content.rendered:
Directed by Shashank Khaitan

Written by Shashank Khaitan

Cast Kiara Advani (Suku). Vicky Kaushal (Govinda Waghmare). Bhumi Pednekar (Gauri Waghmare). Amy Aela (Bijli Actress). Chiranjeev Bedi (Sandy). Viraj Ghelani (Baldev). Anindita Gogoi (Special Appearance). Akkshay Gunaawat (Vishnu). Aseem Hattangadi (Advocate Bhide). Ranbir Kapoor (Special Appearance). Shashank Khaitan (Anand Joshi). Trupti Khamkar (Manju). Veenah Naair (Charulata Vishwakarma). Renuka Shahane (Asha Waghmare). Dayanand Shetty (Inspector Javed Khan). Sayaji Shinde (Ajit Dharkar). Amey Wagh (Kaustubh Godbole)

Language Hindi

Producers Ajit Andhare. Alex Anthony Fernandes. Hiroo Johar. Karan Johar. Punit Kumar. Apoorva Mehta. Somesh Shivraj.

Production Dharma Productions. Mentor Disciple Films. Viacom18 Motion Pictures
